headline: Natalie Knight,  Matthew Ellison
abstract: The bride and groom, both lawyers, met at a bar in Washington.
lead_paragraph: Natalie Jane Knight and Matthew Brandon Ellison are to be married Jan. 19 at the Cedar Room in Charleston, S.C. Patrick Michael Duffy, a retired judge of the United States District Court for the District of South Carolina, for whom the bride clerked from 2017-18, is to officiate.
